CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 7, 1955, pg. 15 reads: "Admiral's Cape -Codder - Many new home owners have found it a pleasure to live in Admiral Cape-Codder like this one in Pittsburgh's Beltzhoover section. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Small cape cod style house with narrow textured brick and small aluminum awning over entryway, Beltzhoover
